description: My Sensei is a skill that you can always some to for a great quote to uplift your spirits. Once the app is started you can ask My Sensei to say a quote or give you wisdom and it will respond with a random quote for you. More quotes will be added weekly.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask my sensei for a quote
Alexa, ask my sensei for wisdom
Alexa, ask my sensei for advice
name: My Sensei
shortDescription: My Sensei is a skill that gives you many inspirational quotes
